* You must have an Opensubtitles Account to use this app.

* Follow : "https://www.opensubtitles.org/en/newuser"   , to register.

* Extract the tar ball (Compressed Archive) to **Home folder**

* Navigate to subseeker folder

* In explorer (File manager window of subseeker folder) , right click and select 'Open in Terminal'

* In the terminal Window type ' sudo python3 Install.py'

* Enter 'y' if asked to install dependencies (external utility packages)

* A login text shows , Enter your opensubtitle username and password there!

* Once the Partial installation complete , a new readme will open with futher instructions!
